http://www.sbsc.org:80/townhall/columnists/duplantier/dupl121595.html 204.71.237.86 19970108213211 text/html 4328
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 21:32:22 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 04-Jun-96 20:07:18 GMT
