<DOCOLDNO>IA025-000265-B013-162</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/townhall/columnists/fumento/fume041796.html 204.71.237.86 19970108213720 text/html 7270
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 21:37:37 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 04-Jun-96 18:57:04 GMT
